title: Eight Seconds - Big Houses [New Wave/New Romantic]
description:
Eight Seconds was a Canadian New Wave/New Romantic band. This is their second and last CD that includes some great songs such as the fantastic "Tell Diane" and "Here Stood Troy". The CD is currently out of print and hard to find.


Eight Seconds:

Bass - March Cesare 
Drums - Scott Milks 
Keyboards, Producer - Frank Levin 
Producer - Paul Northfield 
Vocals, Guitar - Andres Del Castillo
